#: app/templates/admin/index.html:43
msgid "⚠️ Admin Tips"
msgstr "⚠️ Amathiphu Ophakanyisiwe"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:45
msgid ""
"Never run in production with DEBUG enabled. Debug mode exposes internal "
"details and stack traces."
msgstr ""
"Ungalokothi usebenzise ku-production nge-DEBUG ivuliwe. Imodi ye-debug ivula"
" imininingwane yangaphakathi nezilingana zesistimu."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:47
msgid ""
"Always deploy Grylli behind a reverse proxy (e.g. Caddy, Nginx, or Traefik) "
"and serve it over HTTPS. Sensitive user data must be encrypted in transit."
msgstr ""
"Hlala wethula i-Grylli ngemuva kwe-reverse proxy (isb. Caddy, Nginx, noma "
"Traefik) bese uyinikeza nge-HTTPS. Idatha yomsebenzisi ebucayi kufanele "
"ifihliwe uma iba nesiyalu."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:50
msgid ""
"Ensure the data folder (database) is backed up regularly. Backups are stored"
" in the 'backups' folder."
msgstr ""
"Qinisekisa ukuthi ifolda yedatha (iserver) iyekwephula kubanjwa kwakho"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:53
msgid ""
"The uploads folder is shared. To isolate attachments per user, configure "
"host-level directories and access controls."
msgstr ""
"Ifolda yokulayisha iyashopha. Ukuze uzihlukanise izilinganiso zomsebenzisi "
"ngamnye, hlela amafolda ezinga lokuphakela."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:55
msgid ""
"To restore a backup: stop the container, replace the grylli.db file from a "
"backup, and restart."
msgstr ""
"Ukuvuselela isipele: misa isiqukathi, eshintsha i-data/grylli.db ngenye "
"esuka kufolda yezipele, bese uqala isiqukathi kabusha."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:56
msgid ""
"Admins cannot remove their own admin role to prevent accidental lockout."
msgstr ""
"Abaphathi abakwazi ukususa izinga labo wabaPhathi ukuvimbela ukuvalwa "
"okuzenzakalelayo."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:58
msgid ""
"Rate limits and automatic account lockouts are enforced to protect against "
"brute-force login attempts."
msgstr ""
"Izinga lokuhlangula kanye nezivalo zokuzithokozisa akunqunyelwe "
"ngokuzikhandla ukuze kugcinwe ukubamba umuntu ongenayo izinhlanzi."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:60
msgid ""
"Passwords, SMTP credentials, and API tokens are encrypted at rest using "
"Fernet."
msgstr ""
"Amaphasiwebhu, izivakashi ezikhulumayo, namathokheni e-API acutshungulwe "
"ngenzuzo usebenzisa i-Fernet."

